&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Using different Bi-LSTMs to distinguish different node types for neighbors aggregation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;第二步，聚合不同 type 的 neighbor 信息：&lt;/p&gt;
