\mathcal{E}_{v}=\sum_{f_{i} \in \mathcal{F}(v)} \alpha^{v, i} f_{i} \\
\alpha^{v, i}=\frac{\exp \left\{L e a k y \operatorname{ReLU}\left(u^{T}\left[f_{i} \bigoplus f_{1}(v)\right]\right)\right\}}{\left.\sum_{f_{j} \in \mathcal{F}(v)} \exp \left\{\operatorname{LeakyReLU(u^{T}}\left[f_{j} \oplus f_{1}(v)\right]\right)\right\}}
